# Nuxt 3 Development

## Project context

- Nuxt 3 app in `frontend/` with SSR enabled (`nuxt.config.ts`)
- Server routes: `frontend/server/api/home/*`, middleware in `frontend/server/middleware/`
- Page data: composables in `app/composables/pages/` (e.g. `useGuitar`, `useHome`)
- Strapi: fetch via `useStrapiApi` / `server/utils/strapi.ts`, not direct client calls to Strapi
- Components auto-imported from `app/components/` with `U` prefix (`UButton`, `UMoodHero`)
- Images: `@nuxt/image` with ipx provider; remote Strapi domain configured in `nuxt.config.ts`
- SEO: `usePageSeo`; route rules use SWR cache for public pages

